# ARIA (BuildY)

## Static markup

Use **`github.com/fastygo/templ/utils`** ARIA helpers in Go/`helpers.go` (`AriaLabel`, `AriaExpanded`, `AriaControls`, `MergeAttrs`, …) on interactive server-rendered controls (mobile sheet trigger, theme toggle).

## Client behavior

- **`@ui8kit/aria`** pattern: **dialog/sheet** (mobile menu) only, bundled in **`web/static/js/ui8kit.js`** via `scripts/ui8kit-entry.mjs`.
- Markup contract: `data-ui8kit`, `data-ui8kit-dialog-*` — must match manifest.
- After changing hooks or JS bundle: **`bun run build:js`** then **`bun run validate:aria`**.

## Shell patterns in this app

- Mobile nav: `#ui8kit-mobile-sheet-panel`, `#ui8kit-mobile-sheet-trigger`
- Theme: `#ui8kit-theme-toggle`, `#theme-toggle-icon` (updated by `theme.js`)

Add a manifest pattern when introducing a new interactive primitive.
